title: protective Peter fics?
body:
Anyone have a fic where Peter takes care of Tony? Nothing like slash or anything, but where instead of a mentor/mentee or a father/son relationship, Peter is still getting mentored in tech stuff, but otherwise he’s inadvertently become sort of a big brother figure to a man 2.5 times his age. 

I want Peter helping Tony during panic attacks, and doing the whole shovel talk thing to whoever he’s with…I want depressed tony turning to peter for help. I want them to hug, and cry and be stronger for it. I just want super fucking protective peter, and a Tony who needs it; I want a healing tony.
(I’m up for slash too, so if you have any, please tell me, I just wanted platonic right now)

by 8NightLight8

“No.” Peter’s voice snapped like a whip trough the quiet of the room and caused the man to flinch. “No psychologists. I need to deal with this. Alone.”

“But…” Tony was lost for words for a second. “But this is killing you, Peter! You can’t just expect me to sit here and watch while you…” He swallowed. “You can’t do this,” he whispered. “You can’t do this to me.”

(The last part of the My Demons and Your Lullaby series)
